groupNames.valid.zh: 时间轴可以被添加到目标
groupNames.valid.en: Valid: Timelines can be added to the target

groupNames.already-nested.zh: 无效：时间轴已经嵌套在目标中
groupNames.already-nested.en: Invalid: Timelines already nested in the target

groupNames.recursive-structure.zh: 无效：时间轴将生成无限递归

groupNames.duplicate-track-ids.en: Invalid: Timelines have track ids already present in the target

groupNames.duplicate-track-names.zh: 无法复制。时间轴里出现了相同的名称。
groupNames.duplicate-track-names.en: Invalid: Timelines have names already present in the target
